Personal details: Elad David

Exercise name: EX4: Chat Server with select

Submitted files:
chatserver.c - implementaion of a chat server.

The program implements a server that responde using TCP method.
The program supports the functionality of sending messages between client that are connected to the server, 
disconnect from the server (and the group chat), mantaine a queue for the clients and the messages.
The server closes the connection with each client after the client send empty message.
Run the program useing the arg: <port number> .
Stop the running using ctrl + c.
